{"tid":2203380,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"[BNO 的重要]  有個香港女仔曾在埃及坐冤獄","createTime":"2020-09-15T09:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T00:28:18.000Z","uid":289214,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aef568edf8136e498ea6adcd7e19fc905ed00029","tid":2203380,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T09:40:40.000Z","msg":"【有個香港女仔曾在埃及坐冤獄】<br />\n我去埃及潛水時，在紅海小鎮Dahab認識香港女仔Wendy。她幾年前遊非洲，跟一個德國仔相戀，男友留在Dahab教潛水，她在咖啡店兼職。我們用廣東話相認，她帶我回家（如圖）又帶我去玩。<br />\n<br />\nDahab是旅遊勝地，不久大陸女仔單娜又跟媽媽來玩，但幾日後雙雙失蹤了，只有行李在酒店。整個小鎮議論紛紛，身在大陸的單娜爸爸經中國大使館要求埃及政府尋人。<br />\n<br />\nDahab黑警一樣又唔做嘢又唔讀書，居然拘捕Wendy和她男友，要她扮單娜打給爸爸，訛稱自己跟阿媽去了以色列。Wendy拒絕，黑警老屈她將單娜母女拐帶到以色列，總之算在以色列頭上就可以close file。<br />\n<br />\nWendy妹妹不斷央求香港入境處救人，但入境處唯一做的，是介紹一個住在開羅的香港女人給她。這個女人剛巧回港賀國慶（所以我懷疑她是大陸人），在入境處安排下跟Wendy妹妹見面，前後收了10萬蚊港幣，說會找個埃及律師保釋Wendy。<br />\n<br />\n那時 Wendy 已坐了14日冤獄，跟6、7個女囚犯同房，沒有床也沒有蓆，直接睡在地上。她跟男友等到律師保釋（原來每人保釋費只是5000蚊），但一回Dahab又再被捕，黑警怕他們在鎮上揭發濫捕，將他們再關押14日，前前後後坐足一個月冤獄。<br />\n<br />\n不幸中的大幸是Wendy用BNO入境埃及，英國大使館獲悉一個BNO持有人出事，與德國大使館聯手營救，打去不同監獄確認Wendy所在，再由開羅開十幾個鐘車去監獄，最終令這對情侶脫險。<br />\n<br />\n我記得當年她回來告訴我，我連聽都心驚膽戰。當年入境處好歹轉介了一個中間人（雖然呃錢），今天12個香港人關押大陸，香港政府不聞不問。<br />\n<br />\n當一個政府可以漠視市民在外地遇險，昨天是Wendy遭殃，今天到12個港人叫天不應，明天可以是我們去旅行時孤立無援。<br />\n<br />\n英國衛報以British citizen稱呼持BNO的Wendy：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZC8Zx6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZC8Zx6&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=668bb745\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZC8Zx6</a><br />\n12港人關注組專頁：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/save12hkyouths/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsave12hkyouths%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=18af443b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/save12hkyouths/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103976271283239/photos/a.110014810679385/174583794222486/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103976271283239%2Fphotos%2Fa.110014810679385%2F174583794222486%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=7bef8851\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103976271283239/photos/a.110014810679385/174583794222486/</a>"},{"pid":"6bccacf7c80bf1ca88d4749de9aeb5b8740444bb","tid":2203380,"uid":70313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:48:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da39c8a4f1a10f306d28eab96d76bb99da108f65","tid":2203380,"uid":79865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e7b30e01bf02bfff37323b28ffac9e0c1b83fec","tid":2203380,"uid":365109,"like":1,"dislike":45,"score":-44,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2950128b0d3f07d6a94bd9478ebfb9e0a1c93837","tid":2203380,"uid":234695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2e7b30e01bf02bfff37323b28ffac9e0c1b83fec","tid":2203380,"uid":365109,"like":1,"dislike":45,"score":-44,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:53:49.000Z","msg":"有埋source 都話作，定你大陸仔睇唔明英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa756e703a3141f38943432ecac7a2701faa90ee","tid":2203380,"uid":271101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:01:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbe824a6aeb26fdb1363c3164cb5663a9296c1ac","tid":2203380,"uid":365109,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T23:35:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b60838b50b3f15da67987032ca7d0c88940deba","tid":2203380,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bbe824a6aeb26fdb1363c3164cb5663a9296c1ac","tid":2203380,"uid":365109,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aa756e703a3141f38943432ecac7a2701faa90ee","tid":2203380,"uid":271101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e7b30e01bf02bfff37323b28ffac9e0c1b83fec","tid":2203380,"uid":365109,"like":1,"dislike":45,"score":-44,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"